<i>Neka vrsta monstruma</i>

189
00:15:00,247 --> 00:15:03,478
<i>Monstrum je živ</i>

190
00:15:06,847 --> 00:15:09,725
"Došli smo da napravimo
album naših života.

191
00:15:10,087 --> 00:15:12,396
Kroz naša individualna
i kolektivna putovanja,

192
00:15:12,567 --> 00:15:14,080
ponekad kroz bol i konflikte,

193
00:15:14,247 --> 00:15:16,886
otkrili smo istinsko
znacenje porodice.

194
00:15:17,567 --> 00:15:22,240
