da mi prodajemo...

1544
01:59:06,377 --> 01:59:08,811
Mislim da sam pricao ljudima da
prodajemo kucu u Kanzas Sitiju,

1545
01:59:08,977 --> 01:59:12,094
ali, to ne znaci da se
selimo ovamo. U redu?

1546
01:59:12,902 --> 01:59:15,365
I necemo se seliti u San Francisko

1547
01:59:16,249 --> 01:59:20,226
ako s Metalikom tu ne budem radio,

1548
01:59:20,326 --> 01:59:22,571
jer, znate, to mi je...

1549
01:59:22,697 --> 01:59:25,739
Ja samo želim da budem siguran
da ce basista ostati netaknut,

1550
01:59:25,774 --> 01:59:27,839
da cete krenuti na turneju

1551
01:59:27,874 --> 01:59:32,059
